{"title":"Linux下安装OracleJDK","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.008Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/Linux下安装OracleJDK","updated":"2023-07-28T08:54:05.444Z","content":"<p>@<a href=\"Ubantu%E4%B8%8B%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85OracleJDK\">TOC</a></p>\n<p>由于OpenJDK有些功能和OracleJDK不一样，有些开发必须要用到OracleJDK，但OracleJDK的安装较OpenJDK比较麻烦，网上教程各种不一，因此我记录下我的安装步骤，供大家参考。</p>\n<p><strong>具体步骤只有3步：</strong><br>\n1、下载OracleJDK，卸载OpenJDK。<br>\n2、解压至本地，并配置文件，告诉系统OracleJDK在哪。<br>\n3、使配置生效。</p>\n<p><strong>详细操作</strong><br>\n<strong>1、登陆<a href=\"https://www.oracle.com/cn/java/technologies/javase-downloads.html?source=:ow:o:s:nav:062520GlobalNavProductsLang_zh\" target=\"_blank\">Oracle网站</a>，下载你需要的JDK包</strong><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.oracle.com/cn/java/technologies/javase-downloads.html?source=:ow:o:s:nav:062520GlobalNavProductsLang_zh\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.oracle.com/cn/java/technologies/javase-downloads.html?source=:ow:o:s:nav:062520GlobalNavProductsLang_zh</a><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210307103317231.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210307103351810.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n在终端输入以下代码，卸载之前装的OpenJDK，如没有直接跳过此步骤</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#ubantu</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo apt<span class=\"literal\">-get</span> remove openjdk*</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#centos</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo yum <span class=\"literal\">-y</span> remove java*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>2、下载完后解压到本地的某个目录（你想解压到哪就解压到哪）</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210307103727676.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n解压完之后，在终端输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo vim /etc/profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>按  i   进入编辑模式，在文本末尾加上</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">export JAVA_HOME=/root/jdk<span class=\"literal\">-11</span>.<span class=\"number\">0.5</span>（填你刚刚解压的JDK路径，用绝对路径，此文件夹里要包含bin目录）</span><br><span class=\"line\">export CLASSPATH=.:<span class=\"variable\">$JAVA_HOME</span>/lib/tools.jar:<span class=\"variable\">$JAVA_HOME</span>/lib/dt.jar</span><br><span class=\"line\">export PATH=<span class=\"variable\">$PATH:</span><span class=\"variable\">$JAVA_HOME</span>/bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/b61bc7a178264f09b5f19390201663fd.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>按esc键，再输入    ：wq   退出</p>\n<p>注：我装的是jdk11，如果低版本jdk，有jre目录，可以尝试如下代码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">export JAVA_HOME=你刚刚解压的那个地址</span><br><span class=\"line\">export JRE_HOME=<span class=\"variable\">$</span>&#123;JAVA_HOME&#125;/jre</span><br><span class=\"line\">export CLASSPATH=.:<span class=\"variable\">$</span>&#123;JAVA_HOME&#125;/lib:<span class=\"variable\">$</span>&#123;JRE_HOME&#125;/lib</span><br><span class=\"line\">export PATH=<span class=\"variable\">$</span>&#123;JAVA_HOME&#125;/bin:<span class=\"variable\">$PATH</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>3、然后再在命令行输入</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">source /etc/profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>此时系统已经知道OracleJDK已经装好，输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">java <span class=\"literal\">--version</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210307104736561.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n可以看到OracleJDK已经安装成功。</p>\n<p>Ps：有的机器可能查java版本能查的出来，但运行软件时仍提示jdk没有安装，此时可以重启一下机器试试。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"linux修改jar包中的配置文件","link":"2023/07/28/linux修改jar包中的配置文件"},"next":{"title":"Linux下安装并配置MySQL（Ubantu）","link":"2023/07/28/Linux下安装并配置MySQL（Ubantu）"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/Linux下安装OracleJDK/","reading_time":"543 字约 4 分钟"}